{"tid":598722,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG] 水上活動gp (sailing / windsurfing / kayaking / others)","createTime":"2018-03-19T18:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T02:26:10.000Z","uid":89469,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a26a7f9bbb9320b7045fcdfdbbfead5db4214d54","tid":598722,"uid":89469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T18:05:17.000Z","msg":"[TG] 水上活動gp (sailing / windsurfing / kayaking / others)<br />\n<br />\n最近天氣開始轉熱了<br />\n又係玩水上活動既季節<br />\n<br />\n我岩岩學玩(sailing, kayaking)<br />\n康民抽到2046都未有位，包班去學又好難自己湊夠人<br />\n所以想開個新gp<br />\n當係比大家夾下人包班又好，分享下技術又好，組團去log鐘練習又好<br />\n希望之後大家學夠級可以一齊出下旅程玩下，本地又好外地又好<br />\n<br />\n除左以上活動(sailing / windsurfing / kayaking)<br />\n有玩開或對其他水上活動有興趣既，都可以入黎分享下<br />\n其他水上活動我冇乜研究唔知點去入門，所以只list左康民基本果三項<br />\n<br />\n歡迎有玩過 或 未玩過但有興趣既人加入<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/upwatersports\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fupwatersports&d=2KT%2Fi5ksLszG0e%2B25fHiFIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=04a19f18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/upwatersports</a>"},{"pid":"3bfa4bab4901ba131f61882b5baeed14600a61b6","tid":598722,"uid":89469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T02:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74e2436a87f041e1bd446fbc23b06e80dd7863c","tid":598722,"uid":86696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T03:59:13.000Z","msg":"玩緊龍舟"},{"pid":"3c51ccb2f51b3ea58abeb133b39826c694a04e50","tid":598722,"uid":89469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5a817487f85493242158f9c187583cabc8bff9","tid":598722,"uid":89469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e6c3d19fe5d0dd722ce59e38578353268cde56","tid":59